Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:19.91,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to be \Nlike this, head in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:26.25,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Struggling to escape from \Nthis saturated world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:32.01,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Time passes like whispering sand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.72,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,These circumstances, unchanging
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.72,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,gazing out at a dreamless tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:45.81,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna say goodbye to the \Nconfusion of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:51.23,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I try reaching out, as if to resist
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:56.95,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,We cry millions of times \Nand then get born again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:00.16,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with these red eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.37,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,to that pictured future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:08.96,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Come here right by me, \NI'm clapping my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.05,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:15.42,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Strain my eyes in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:21.06,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see anything, don't know \Nanything, but I'll still go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:27.39,Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,To the place of shining \Nlight in which you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.98,Episode Num,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.98,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}House{\b0}, Unmasked
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.98,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi’s\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Ango Detective Stories)\N"Shoplifting Family" and "Masked Mansion"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:31.65,Main Dialog Italic,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,This is a curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.32,Main Dialog Italic,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suggesting the cursed father \Nand son were both murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.65,Main Dialog Italic,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the famous detective, \NYuuki Shinjurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.20,Main Dialog Italic,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Mystery of the masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:40.24,Main Dialog Italic,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I was overlooking something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.74,Main Dialog Italic,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The murderer is in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:47.96,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}is{\i0} the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:48.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in trying to \Ndeceive me now, Sasa Kazamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hayami Seigen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Director of the Security Bureau \NMetropolitan Police Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Koyama Izumi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Public Prosecutor\N Joint Coordinating Dept.\N Public Prosecutor's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Itoji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Widow of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Sasa Fumihiko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Son of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Mitsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter of the Late Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Sasa Kigihiko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Younger Brother of the \NLate Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Detective's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.50,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kaishou Rie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.50,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kaishou Rinroku's Daughter\NLives at Home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.00,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.00,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:59.01,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? \NSasa Kazamori was the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.93,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,No one's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:03.72,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.56,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.18,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Detective, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.27,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be better off asking \Nyour mother and uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.94,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.70,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.58,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,I've known it for years \Nnow. There is no Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.33,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.08,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you killed \NBrother a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.37,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.21,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.38,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.67,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,A RAI, created by Komamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:41.09,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,The program that can imitate humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.35,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,When necessary, it made an appearance \Nby inhabiting this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:50.48,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it was like that, entering \Ndevices throughout the house, watching us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.69,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Kazamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:55.98,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,...is a program?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.78,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Taku wasn't a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.74,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,He was a maintenance technician,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.74,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,hired by Komamori to keep \NKazamori in good working order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.49,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,When I confronted him, \Nhe quickly confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.49,Name,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Taku Hidenobu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.49,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Live-in Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.00,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,You knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.83,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.50,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... I mean, \NKazamori was a machine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.92,Main Dialog,Fumihiko,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave Dad's fortune \Nand company in his hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.01,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It was more convenient that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.89,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,We stumbled to the truth \Nof Kazamori's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.51,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,after my brother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.73,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,But by then, Kazamori had \Nalready been acknowledged
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.48,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,as the president of the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.90,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would've \Nhappened if he'd been exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:37.57,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,The value of the company \Nwould've plummeted,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.40,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,and even if we'd be able \Nto collect the inheritance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.53,Main Dialog,Kigihiko,0000,0000,0000,,we'd have to pay tax on it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.57,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, by leaving \NKazamori as President,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:48.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,you two were able to operate \Nfreely in his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.54,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you stayed silent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.33,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Fumihiko and I always thought \Nthis... was our brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:03.34,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,You're fools for not noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.39,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.35,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,It was this country that \Noutlawed my husband's research!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:11.02,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, according to \Nexisting law, only humans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.56,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,are allowed to collect inheritances \Nand represent companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:17.44,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,A thorough investigation will \Nbe made in those regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.65,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,However... There's one \Nthing I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:23.20,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Who died?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.91,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,All we know from the coroner's report
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:29.37,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,is that the victim was a \NJapanese male in his late 20's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.41,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Taku called the victim Kazamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.50,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,On the spur of the moment, \NI went along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.04,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if that corpse \Nwere accepted as Kazamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.88,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,then Fumihiko would be able \Nto inherit everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.76,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't murder anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.89,Main Dialog,Itoji,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone did any killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.43,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Kazamori, you're \Ncoming to the station
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.39,Main Dialog,Hayami,0000,0000,0000,,as a suspect in the murder \Nof an unknown victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.61,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shinjurou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.49,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.83,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Handle that gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.62,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It's a valuable program.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.87,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.04,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still exercising \Nthe right to silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.55,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,...Kazamori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.21,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:27.76,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a detective and \Nthis is my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.93,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take me out of there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.02,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,knowing that I transferred \Nto this doll's data bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.23,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,After all, if we'd left you there, \Nyou would've been arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your data still in \Nthat refrigerator, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.98,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I deleted it the moment I \Ntransferred to this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.99,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, I destroyed all \Nof the data banks in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.57,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I was originally made \Nas a consumer product,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.78,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,so my specs don't allow me to be copied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:59.04,Main Dialog Italic,Refrigerator,0000,0000,0000,,Think about a more nutritional \Nbalance, such as toast or fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.42,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Komamori was the only \Nengineer who could create
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.63,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,artificial intelligence that \Nperfectly copied human thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:12.51,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Kaishou Rinroku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:12.51,Name Sub,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Chairman of JJ Systems
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.05,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,What made him brilliant was how he \Ndispersed a huge quantity of data
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.43,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,to the world's networks as an \Nomnipresent distributed system,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:18.69,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,where only the main controlling \Nprogram is held in the actual body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.23,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,If it was just the main program, \Nhe could even download it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.36,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,to this refrigerator, say, or \Na cell phone's memory bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.36,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you realize the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:33.45,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That Kazamori was the RAI program \Ncreated by Sasa Komamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.95,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:40.08,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,RAI is outlawed under the New \NInformation Privacy and Protection Act
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.29,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,and as such, may no longer \Nbe manufactured or sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.63,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew of the existence of such \Ntech, I would report it to you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.76,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:52.93,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you think a RAI \Ncould kill someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:56.60,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... That's a difficult question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.77,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the identity \Nof the charred corpse is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.60,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,There's a simple way to learn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:06.02,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,How about running a DNA test?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.90,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Checking it against our \Ncriminal database? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.49,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm sure the case \Nwill eventually be reported
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.83,Main Dialog,Rinroku,0000,0000,0000,,as Kazamori committing suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.46,Main Dialog Italic,Woman A,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.17,Main Dialog Italic,Woman A,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:36.05,Main Dialog,Chief Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,As you have clearly seen from the video \Nevidence, RAI robots in circulation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:41.52,Main Dialog,Chief Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,are being used for wanton cruelty or \Nsatisfying the desires of sexual deviants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.10,Main Dialog,Chief Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived at the conclusion \Nthat this technology
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.15,Main Dialog,Chief Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,is interfering with the wholesome \Nupbringing of young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.77,Main Dialog,Reporter,0000,0000,0000,,Will they be banned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.15,Main Dialog,Chief Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,Even sterner measures will be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.99,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,The New Information Privacy and \NProtection Act is an evil law
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.70,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,that was obviously created \Njust to outlaw my RAI!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.95,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask this:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.50,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Who has RAI hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:04.17,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,What's the harm in taking pleasure \Nfrom watching RAI bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:09.09,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,destroy each other or even \Nmake love to each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.80,Main Dialog Italic,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,They're not humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.93,Main Dialog Italic,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,As shown in the clip, Mr. \NSasa asserts that RAI users
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:15.97,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Komamori, Creator of RAI\N "The New Information Privacy and Protection Act is an evil law"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.97,Main Dialog Italic,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,are free to do what they \Nplease with their robots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.51,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Person or Machine?\NLegal regulations are necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.51,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Exclusive\NShocking scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.51,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}That idol is hooked!\NRAI Love
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.51,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest... it's a \Nlittle grotesque, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.64,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But the RAI only do \Nwhat they're ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:29.11,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't believe that my brother, \NKazamori, would murder someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:36.03,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Prosecutor Koyama sent us \Nto confiscate evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.12,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, right now, my mother and \Nbrother are with the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.04,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.47,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.35,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the last RAI in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.35,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I must continue my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.65,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something \NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.03,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.15,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,My thanks for getting \Nme out of there safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.24,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,A little bonus for a job well \Ndone? But with that body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.83,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to satisfy no \Nmatter what body I am in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:30.67,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,The data that is my true form is \Ndispersed in computers all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.92,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,where it lives like a parasite \Nand continues to grow, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.88,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,What do humans want to know? \NWhat should they become?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:40.14,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,And what are they looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.60,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Squeeze! Tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.94,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Pull off my arms. Crush my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.11,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Tear me into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.90,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:05.75,Main Dialog,Woman Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Shinjurou can't be \Nsatisfied by anyone other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.79,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.71,Main Dialog,Woman Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You've got all the knowledge in the \Nworld at your disposal, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.05,Main Dialog,Woman Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Why not run a search?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.84,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:19.63,Main Dialog,Woman Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I eat souls, the feelings \Nleft by humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.10,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to eat me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.26,Main Dialog,Woman Inga,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.14,Main Dialog,Woman Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me. Who is that corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:33.52,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! It must not work on \Nhim 'cause he's not a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.78,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you covering for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:39.49,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:44.28,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I'm not a person, but \Na RAI, prohibited by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:45.70,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,So why would you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.66,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori... You don't lie, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You've been telling just \Nthe truth this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.67,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you should also really be \Nable to say whether you killed a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't say \Nanything. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.31,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,Public Security Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.53,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.16,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are the city's \Nsecurity, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.33,Main Dialog,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki Shinjurou...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.71,Main Dialog,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,Did you take something \Nout of the Sasa house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:35.17,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.42,Main Dialog,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.42,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Who the burned man was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.30,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't someone from in the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.05,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,it had to be someone \Nwho came from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:47.01,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What I wanted to know was \Nwhich group he belonged to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.10,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The Public Security Force is a militia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.06,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,that's still under the \Ndirection of the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:55.90,Main Dialog,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the rumors of you being a \Ndetective who always fails are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.19,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.20,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The war has come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.66,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor's in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.08,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,He must've known the truth \Nabout Kazamori, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.87,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! The doctor's been burned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.33,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.88,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.67,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Move! We're with the \Nprosecutor's office!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.92,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The prosecutor's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:25.93,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,During the war, the prosecutor's \Noffice had deep connections
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.89,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,to domestic politics, and \Ntheir power expanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't know you were \Nallowed to carry guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.23,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.07,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,That corpse came from \Noutside, the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.15,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.70,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.50,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,He's a RAI?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.72,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor wasn't human either...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.56,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Koyama with the Public Prosecutor's \NOffice, Joint Coordinating Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:15.81,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,To identify the wartime identity \Nof the man who was burned to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.10,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,his DNA was checked against the data \Nof every registered civil servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.94,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,...and a match was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:24.49,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us wants that to go public.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:25.90,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.53,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,And in exchange, you're going \Nto take that thing away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:30.07,Main Dialog,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:34.12,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you like. You're \Nthe ones who failed first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.42,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Izumi-chan, that was so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.30,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.80,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even Dr. Taku...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:53.22,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If the charred corpse wasn't \NKazamori, a new question is raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.73,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,What's the identity of the corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.19,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And how was he set on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:04.23,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,If a mechanical body held fast \Nto him and set him afire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.61,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then Kazamori's program \Nentered this body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.99,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.53,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But this thing moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.33,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then one more RAI?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:17.08,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,No. Kazamori said he was the last RAI.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.46,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And he doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.96,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then who's controlling this body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.34,Main Dialog Italic,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant deductions, \NDefeated Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.80,Main Dialog Italic,Taku,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but would \Nyou bring me Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.36,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you back, Kazamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.53,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,At this distance, even \Nwireless, there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:56.16,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kazamori. Return to your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.42,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.58,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:06.13,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... Are you Sasa Komamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.17,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.30,Name White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sasa Komamori
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.30,Name Sub White,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Creator of RAI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.80,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Mitsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.89,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,F-Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.72,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,What are you crying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:23.15,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,After all... I thought you \Ndied seven years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.15,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:29.99,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I watched you through \NTaku's eyes every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.74,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't feel like \Nit's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.66,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you done this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.83,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Kaishou's \Ndaughter, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.41,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is our first meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.17,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so foolishly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.75,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you die in an explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.84,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,You deceived Mitsuko-san and \Nthe rest of your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.59,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,and Kazamori-san was a RAI, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.09,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:56.60,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the real aim of the New \NInformation Privacy and Protection Act?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.43,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,You're a public prosecutor, \Nright? What have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.81,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.52,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,...the RAI that you developed was \Nbeing used for murderous games
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.27,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and other affronts to public \Norder and standards of decency,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.57,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,which was having an effect \Non young people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.49,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,That's only the excuse they used!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:15.32,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,They banned the distribution of RAI \Nbecause they wanted to have a monopoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.20,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,For military use...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.87,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,For military use?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:22.87,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,True, it would be possible for superior \NAI to be put to use as weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.75,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I made it look like I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:26.96,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why go that far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.55,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.05,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,If my RAI had been used in the war, \Nthere would've been even more casualties,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.43,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,both enemies and allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.01,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:41.18,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But the intelligence service \Ndidn't give up on RAI.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.98,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,And two nights ago, a spy finally \Nbroke through your security system
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.27,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and entered the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.40,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,One man who had no business being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,So he had to have come from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:58.07,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't know right away \Nif he was police or military.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.37,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,A spy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.54,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,His DNA matched with a member of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.54,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,the Self-Defense Force's Insurrection \NCountermeasures Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:09.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed the intruder and burned \Nhim to death to cover your tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:16.13,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,They came after all this time, \Nthinking I might still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.47,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,But Kazamori found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.14,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to say that \NKazamori killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:25.48,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about the real Dr. Taku,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:28.06,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,whose remains were most likely \Ntaken for yours seven years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:32.90,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,What if I said that Kazamori \Nkilled him, too, on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.11,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna blame \Neverything on Kazamori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.78,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I made Kazamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.58,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I can do with him as I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.12,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:47.21,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I make you sick? I often \Nheard that seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.71,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,There were many people who \Nwould kill or rape robots
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:55.38,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,that had my RAI installed, and worse \Nthings I dare not even speak of!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:18:00.09,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,But all humans more or less \Ngo whole hog in their pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:03.77,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,of what they take to \Nbe beautiful or fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:07.56,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,If this single-mindedness is exerted \Non another person, it's a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.27,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,But we're talking about robots here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.15,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,So who gets hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:16.03,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,"Makes me sick" is silly talk from \Nsomeone who won't recognize his own desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I was... on a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.20,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a lot of different things there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:24.54,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,So I think I understand \Nwhat you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.54,Main Dialog,Rie,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:29.50,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Humans love beautiful \Nthings and fun things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:34.13,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,We love extravagances and luxuries, \Nso when a scientific genius
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:37.76,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,translates our ideals into reality, \Nit's like the nouveau riche
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,building a mansion; Everyone's \Ntrue character is revealed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:42.18,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and no one should be scorned \Nfor it in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.68,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:50.14,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,I was just looking for something \Nbeautiful to love and fun to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:53.56,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,This is a much more honest \Nway to go about it than war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.90,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Just as humans love beautiful \Nand enjoyable things
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.15,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,and luxuries, there's one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.28,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,The love of what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:04.41,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,What's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Call it justice if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:10.58,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Men love beautiful women, women \Nlook for extravagances...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.29,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,People are beings where a love \Nof what's right goes hand in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.38,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,with a desire to do all \Nmanner of evil acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.71,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,And what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:22.26,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, when Itoji and Kigihiko were \Nabout to be blamed for the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.39,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,a surveillance camera made \Na sound, and as a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.47,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,the two of them were proven innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:32.48,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,You did that, didn't you, Kazamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:35.27,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.94,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Idiotic! Why would he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.69,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.58,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Kazamori did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.04,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So the wrong people \Nwouldn't be arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.21,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has desires they \Ncan't tell anyone about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.88,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:57.09,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,But where is your sense of what's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:03.26,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Kazamori, did you kill anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:04.97,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:10.73,Main Dialog Italic,Kazamori,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:16.40,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be reported that \NKazamori committed suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:20.07,Main Dialog,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,but you're going to be taken into \Ncustody by the Joint Coordinating Dept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.21,Main Dialog,Komamori,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was break what I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.71,Main Dialog,Mitsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.56,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kaishou, please remember \Nwhat you promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.44,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I should've eaten that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.32,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.82,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Shinjurou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.07,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,Kazamori, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.95,Main Dialog,Android,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.79,Main Dialog,Shinjurou,0000,0000,0000,,We're just living... and falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.59,Main Dialog,Android,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:36.14,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,In the pale morning \Nmist, a whispered prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:44.15,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna follow this \Ntwisted landscape with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:52.16,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for the "truth", \N"a 'lie' will do" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:22:00.58,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tracing it as if we can see through
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:04.46,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, beyond words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:08.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a falling feather
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.47,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:16.89,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:36.33,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, unravel it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:40.46,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Like a tattered cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:43.29,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for, find it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:48.51,Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,So we can cuddle close together here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.01,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode is inspired by a \Nstory called "The Phantom Tower",
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:55.47,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,from "Meiji-era Ango Detective Stories".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.47,0:22:56.89,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read the story out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:22:58.31,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.85,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The name Shimada \NIkunoshin has been changed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:03.52,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,into Shimada Hakurou for the manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:04.23,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:06.82,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the one we're in \Ncalled a "TV manga"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:11.32,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-chan said that if you read \N"Noitamina" backwards, it means "TV manga".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:12.16,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:17.16,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't trust bureaucrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.29,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on UN-GO, \N"The Phantom Statue"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.29,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Phantom Statue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:21.29,Source,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by Ango Sakaguchi’s\NMeijikaika Ango Torimonochou\N(Meiji-era Ango Detective Stories)\N"The Phantom Tower"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:23.87,Main Dialog,Inga,0000,0000,0000,,And why did that name chan-
